  "body": "please allow for a CLI parameter to let lighthouse to use a different data directory for the 4844 data.\r\n\r\neg\r\n\r\n./lighthouse bn --4844-data-dir /path/to/4844storage  \r\n\r\nReason: The 4844 data structure is designed to not be processed and rather just be temporarily stored. Further this data should have a low disk read write access requirement so another non-SSD media could be used. \r\n\r\n@realbigsean ",
